overview.en: TBOS tokens is the token of Treasure Blockchain Operating System with a total amount of 8.4 billion, which will never be additionally issued; in TBOS platform, users to make the whole ecology healthier and have more development motivation. TBOS strives to promote the popularity of blockchain applications.We hope our efforts open a new window for the world, and become a social practice of great significance.We use a better user experience and incentives to ensure the growth and sustainability of TBOS.
overview.zh: TBOS通证是宝藏区块链操作系统的代币，总量为84亿，将永远不会额外发行； 在TBOS平台上，用户可以使整个生态系统更加健康，并具有更大的发展动力。 TBOS致力于促进区块链应用的普及，希望我们的努力为世界打开一个新的窗口，并成为具有重要意义的社会实践。我们使用更好的用户体验和激励机制，以确保TBOS的增长和可持续性。
